sequenceDiagram
    actor A as Student A
    actor B as Student B
    participant Session as CollaborationSession
    participant Sync as StateStore / StatePatch
    participant Mail as peer mailboxes

    A->>Session: join shared project
    B->>Session: join shared project

    A->>Session: applyChange(methods/main, say("alpha"), t=10)
    Session->>Sync: compare timestamp + version
    Sync-->>Session: accepted
    Session->>Mail: queue change for B

    B->>Session: applyChange(methods/main, say("beta"), t=10, change-a)
    Session->>Sync: same-timestamp conflict
    Sync-->>Session: reject / supersede

    B->>Session: applyChange(methods/main, pointAt(target), t=10, change-c)
    Session->>Sync: last-write-wins tie-break by changeId
    Sync-->>Session: document version++
    Session->>Mail: queue accepted change for A

    A->>Mail: pull pending changes
    B->>Mail: pull pending changes
    Session-->>A: synced document + presence
    Session-->>B: synced document + presence
